<item>
            <title>[SPR-2167] ClassLoader handling for schema and handler resources is inconsistent</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-2167</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Spring does not correctly delegate lookups for schema and handler resources to the ApplicationContext classloader if set. Futhermore the handling is different between DefaultNamespaceHandlerResolver &amp;amp; PluggableSchemaResolver in XmlBeanDefinitionReader.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I will attach a patch that fixes the issue for me.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
